{
  "stem": "3631.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You saw in the picture, in the movie, where they threw the luggage out of the-- from down from the-- from the catwalk from the, from the deck.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went door by door, and we and the whole family were pushed down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in the Plac Zgody, the one square in, in the ghetto where they assembled people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the place was full, they pulled up the trucks and they took them to the trains to send out east.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my parents, my sister, and I were down there and just so happened that one German saw somebody who knew me from my work came and said to me, Dressler, [GERMAN], what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a stupid question, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, where is your family?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, come with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he called another German over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he moved us over to a small square, maybe the size of this room and he said, you stay here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, why he did it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not friendly with him, or so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just knew me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The strange thing in this was, my sister had a girlfriend who stood with us and she-- as he started, she, she had her hand, her arm, on my sister's.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he said, come with me, she went with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that point, this saved her life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it shows how, how, how much your life was worth was an instant, a, a little moment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we stood there on that square that was in front of an orphanage, or of a children's home.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
